Champions League semi-final line-up confirmed . 
  Real Madrid and Juventus will face Barcelona and Bayern Munich in the last four of the competition . 
  Juventus beat Monaco 1-0 on aggregate in the quarter-finals . 
  Bayern Munich beat Porto 2-1 in the second leg of the last-16 . 
  Cristiano Ronaldo and Co will play in the final in Berlin on June 6 . 
 